12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 1-124, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 1-124. A. Unless otherwise specifically defined, "per-
16 pupil expenditure" shall mean the aggregate current expenditures of
17 school districts, from all funding sources including federal funds,
18 state funds and local funds, plus the direct support aggregate
19 current expenditures of the state for the day-to-day operations of
20 schools and school districts from all funding sources including
21 federal funds, divided by the aggregate student membership number
22 for the same fiscal year for which the expenditures are determined.
23 The aggregate student membership number shall be the count of
24 students enrolled on October 1 or the school day closest to October
