14 6. 8. Support services for business;
15 7. 9. Operation and maintenance of plant services;
16 8. 10. Student transportation services;
17 9. 11. Child nutrition services; and
18 10. 12. Enterprise services.
19 B. Aggregate current expenditures shall not include
20 expenditures for adult and community education, facilities
21 acquisition and construction services, debt services, property, and
22 other expenditures not related to the day-to-day operations.
23 C. The provisions of subsection A of this section shall apply
24 when related to the expenditure of public funds by educational and
